---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Ariff Mohamed - Azure Cloud Solutions Engineer" description="Expert Azure cloud solutions engineer specializing in security, automation, and compliance.">
  <div style="min-height: 100vh; display: grid; grid-template-rows: auto 1fr auto; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; color: #333; background: #f8f9fa;">
    
    <!-- Header -->
    <header style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0066cc, #004499); color: white; padding: 2rem 1rem; text-align: center;">
      <h1 style="font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0; line-height: 1.2;">Ariff Mohamed</h1>
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 400; margin: 0; opacity: 0.9;">Azure Cloud Solutions Engineer | Security Specialist</h2>
    </header>
    
    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main style="flex: 1; padding: 3rem 1rem;">
      
      <!-- Hero Section -->
      <section style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto 4rem auto; text-align: center;">
        <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: #555;">Transforming enterprise cloud infrastructure with security-first Azure architecture and innovative automation solutions. Currently advancing cybersecurity expertise at MIT.</p>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
          <a href="#projects" style="background: #0066cc; color: white; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; transition: background 0.2s;">View Projects</a>
          <a href="#about" style="background: white; color: #0066cc; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; border: 2px solid #0066cc; transition: all 0.2s;">Learn More</a>
        </div>
      </section>
      
      <!-- Projects Section -->
      <section id="projects" style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto 4rem auto;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 700; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #333;">Featured Azure Projects</h2>
        <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.125rem; color: #666; margin-bottom: 3rem; max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">Explore my specialized Azure implementations focused on automation, security, and enterprise management</p>
        
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 2rem; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
          <div style="background: white; border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">
            <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 1rem 0; color: #333;">Azure Automation Hub</h3>
            <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Comprehensive PowerShell runbook automation platform for enterprise user management, resource provisioning, and operational workflows. Features advanced scheduling, error handling, and audit trails.</p>
            <a href="https://automation.aglobaltec.com" target="_blank" style="color: #0066cc; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500;">Explore Automation ‚Üí</a>
          </div>
          
          <div style="background: white; border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">
            <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 1rem 0; color: #333;">Log Analytics Toolkit</h3>
            <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Advanced KQL query library and monitoring dashboard suite for Azure security insights, performance analysis, and compliance reporting. Real-time alerting and custom workbooks included.</p>
            <a href="https://log.aglobaltec.com" target="_blank" style="color: #0066cc; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500;">Explore Analytics ‚Üí</a>
          </div>
          
          <div style="background: white; border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">
            <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 1rem 0; color: #333;">Secure Storage Patterns</h3>
            <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Enterprise-grade Azure storage security implementations featuring encryption at rest and in transit, compliance frameworks, access policies, and data governance best practices.</p>
            <a href="https://storage.aglobaltec.com" target="_blank" style="color: #0066cc; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500;">Explore Storage ‚Üí</a>
          </div>
          
          <div style="background: white; border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;">
            <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 1rem 0; color: #333;">Device Compliance Monitor</h3>
            <p style="color: #666; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Microsoft Intune-powered device management and compliance monitoring solution. Automated policy enforcement, security baselines, and comprehensive reporting for enterprise endpoints.</p>
            <a href="https://compliance.aglobaltec.com" target="_blank" style="color: #0066cc; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500;">Explore Compliance ‚Üí</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      
      <!-- About Section -->
      <section id="about" style="max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 700; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; color: #333;">About Me</h2>
        
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 3rem; align-items: start;">
          <div>
            <p style="font-size: 1.125rem; color: #666; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">As an Azure Cloud Solutions Engineer specializing in security architecture, I bring deep technical expertise in enterprise cloud infrastructure, automation, and compliance. My experience spans large-scale Azure implementations, security frameworks, and innovative problem-solving for complex business challenges.</p>
            
            <p style="font-size: 1.125rem; color: #666; line-height: 1.6;">Currently advancing my expertise through MIT's Cybersecurity program, I'm passionate about developing secure, scalable Azure solutions that drive business value while maintaining the highest security and compliance standards.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: #0066cc;">Azure Specializations</h3>
            <div style="display: grid; gap: 0.75rem;">
              <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; color: #666;">
                <span style="width: 8px; height: 8px; background: #0066cc; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;"></span>
                Azure Security Architecture
              </div>
              <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; color: #666;">
                <span style="width: 8px; height: 8px; background: #0066cc; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;"></span>
                PowerShell Automation & Runbooks
              </div>
              <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; color: #666;">
                <span style="width: 8px; height: 8px; background: #0066cc; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;"></span>
                KQL & Log Analytics
              </div>
              <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; color: #666;">
                <span style="width: 8px; height: 8px; background: #0066cc; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;"></span>
                Microsoft Intune Management
              </div>
              <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; color: #666;">
                <span style="width: 8px; height: 8px; background: #0066cc; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;"></span>
                Storage Security & Encryption
              </div>
              <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; color: #666;">
                <span style="width: 8px; height: 8px; background: #0066cc; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;"></span>
                Compliance & Governance
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      
    </main>
    
    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer style="background: #333; color: white; text-align: center; padding: 2rem 1rem;">
      <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Get In Touch</h3>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem; opacity: 0.8;">Interested in Azure cloud security solutions or enterprise automation projects?</p>
      
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 2rem; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 2rem auto;">
        <a href="mailto:ariff@aglobaltec.com" style="color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 1rem; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); border-radius: 8px; transition: background 0.2s;">
